o read the full article</a></div><br></div><hr><div class='item'><h2><a href="https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2023/aug/07/biden-administration-lawsuit-cbp-one-app" target="_blank">Biden administration sued over asylum appointment app that ‘does not work’</a></h2><div class="description"> CBP One requirement creates unlawful hurdle for migrants on app riddled with glitches and indecipherable error messages, suit says. Immigrant rights advocates and asylum seekers filed a lawsuit against Customs and Border Protection last week. They claim federal officials have created a new hurdle for people seeking asylum in the United States.</div><br><span class="date"><strong>Published on:</strong> Mon, 07 Aug 2023 10:00:38 GMT</span><br><div class="category"><strong>Category: </strong><span class="category-text">world</span></div><br><div class="source"><strong>Source: </strong><span class="source-text">The Guardian</span></div><br><div class="link"><a href="https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2023/aug/07/biden-administration-lawsuit-cbp-one-app" target="_blank">Click here to read the full article</a></div><br></div><hr><div class='item'><h2><a href="https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2023/aug/07/republicans-fentanyl-biden-asylum-seekers-cynicism" target="_blank">Republicans accused of cynical ploy in blaming fentanyl crisis on Biden</a></h2><div class="description"> Critics say GOP leaders misrepresent asylum seekers as being behind smuggling of opioid that kills 70,000 Americans a year. Republicans accused of exploiting tragedy of America's fentanyl crisis by blaming Joe Biden for rising death toll. Critics say Republican leaders are guilty of a cynical political ploy by misrepresenting an increase in asylum seekers.</div><br><span class="date"><strong>Published on:</strong> Mon, 07 Aug 2023 10:00:37 GMT</span><br><div class="category"><strong>Category: </strong><span class="category-text">world</span></div><br><div class="source"><strong>Source: </strong><span class="sou